message.body: Hey it's Julian. I have a huge mushroom growing medium someone gave me as a gift that I don't want. Do you want to take it? Think it grows oysters.
It's big, we don't have the fridge space.
You just spray it twice a day, some mushroom farm ppl sell them
Also have some rice bran oil I don't want if you're into that. Big bottle
Ok I'll take those things. Do you guys want some veggie sausages?
Cool, yeah we eat those. I can bring them by if you're around in a little, or sometime this week. No rush.
